Package: assignmentB2
Title: Create summary statistics and boxplot across groups
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yitong",
           family = "Zhao",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "imyitong.zhao@gmail.com")
Description: This package contains a function `summary_and_boxplot_by_group()` that calculates the summary statistics (min, max, mean, median) of a variable in a data frame
    across different groups. It also creates a boxplot where x-axis represents groups and y-axis represents the variable.
